Name: optic nerve glioma
Definition: A movement disorder that causes involuntary tremors

Name: optic nerve sheath meningioma
Definition: An endometrial carcinoma that derives_from squamous cells and gland-like cells.

Definition: An endometrial carcinoma that derives_from squamous cells and gland-like cells.

Name: anterior optic tract meningioma
Definition: A malignant ovarian germ cell neoplasm that is a teratoma containing variable amounts of immature (typically primitive/embryonal neuroectodermal) tissues
